window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Six years ago the woman Carter Blake loved disappeared and told him not to ever look for her. For six long years, he kept that promise. She was a woman on the run - a woman with a secret many would kill for. It was better that she stay hidden. </p> <p>But now someone else is looking for her. Trenton Gage is a hit man with a talent for finding people - dead or alive. And his next job is to track down the woman Carter Blake once loved, a woman on the run. With both men hunting the same person, the question is, who will find her first? </p>"; 
